The paper discusses a framework for evaluating and improving first-order ontologies using automated theorem provers, which is a topic related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of competency questions to evaluate ontologies also relates to natural language processing (cs.CL) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of WordNet and ontology mapping, which are topics related to databases (cs.DB).
